# Exercise 2/ Lab 1 - Semaphore

This project shows an implementation of a custom Semaphore class

## Requirements
- Compatible with **Linux** only
- A C++11 compiler
- The MakeFile

## Install
2. Go to Exercises/ directory: cd Exercise Two_Semaphores
3. Build project: make CLEAN && make
4. Run: ./main.out

## Project/files Content
- **Sempahore:** implementation of a Semaphore
- **main.cpp:** the traditional start point of the program, showing off the semaphore implementation

